:44:53.000Z","msg":"個名係0幾年果陣支那註冊先，無印又真係冇得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯apple當年都用好撚多錢係台灣買過名"},{"pid":"11150cba0b1d28cff0133605b73913f664732b8c","tid":891732,"uid":75745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"改做無良印品咪唔告你囉"},{"pid":"b8bd6ac95608b65a449ddfd1d02ceb6b9a93338a","tid":891732,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11150cba0b1d28cff0133605b73913f664732b8c","tid":891732,"uid":75745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"改做無良印品咪唔告你囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:54:03.000Z","msg":"改無一良品好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66242cfe539b2a18c134fef8cf3925febfaa74d","tid":891732,"uid":76216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8bafacc0cfc9ba330cd96ba04b0ce52f624d00c","tid":891732,"uid":154385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T11:04:10.000Z","msg":"王老吉事件2"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:14:47.000Z","msg":"法官  ： 打和啦"},{"pid":"3e09171f0a2d9a43e0f88659457b0d781b7108b3","tid":891732,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"日本仔有呢個無大陸仔有呢個无洗撚理咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣一睇就知邊個老翻啦"}]}